headline: DuPont and Habitat for Humanity International continue global partnership
summary: Habitat for Humanity International and DuPont today announced they are renewing their annual global partnership. As part of the collaboration, DuPont will donate products to local Habitat for Humanity affiliates as well as provide cash donations that support employee volunteer builds around the world.
